Cream of rice with protein and IMO Syrup

How to make:
1) Get a pot with a large area
2) Put 100g of rice of your choosing into the pot
3) Pour 2.5 times water of the amount of rice in the cup
4) Cover the pot and put it on high heat
5) After water starts boiling, put on low heat and mix the rice every minute or so
6) When water is nearly completely absorbed and rice starts sticking the the pot, turn off the heat and cover the pot for about 5 minutes
7) Pour 45g of protein onto rice
8) Mix the two using a mixing machine
9) Take out of the pot into a bowl
10) Pour IMO syrup onto the dish
11) Eat
